### Telegram Authentication Test

### 1. Send OTP to Telegram Username
POST http://localhost:3000/client/telegram-auth/send-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "johndoe"
}

### 2. Verify Telegram OTP
POST http://localhost:3000/client/telegram-auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "johndoe",
  "otp_code": "12345"
}

### 3. Authenticate with Telegram
POST http://localhost:3000/client/telegram-auth/authenticate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 123456789,
  "first_name": "John",
  "last_name": "Doe",
  "username": "johndoe",
  "photo_url": "https://t.me/i/userpic/320/johndoe.jpg",
  "auth_date": 1640995200,
  "hash": "test_hash_for_demo"
}

### 4. Get User Profile (requires authentication)
GET http://localhost:3000/client/telegram-auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 5. Update User Profile (requires authentication)
PUT http://localhost:3000/client/telegram-auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "phone_number": "+998901234567",
  "date_of_birth": "1990-01-01",
  "gender": "male",
  "nationality": "Uzbek",
  "passport_number": "AA1234567",
  "home_country": "Uzbekistan",
  "home_city": "Tashkent"
}

### 6. Refresh Token
POST http://localhost:3000/client/telegram-auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh_token": "{{refreshToken}}"
}
